props.description:
a map of event names and their phase name. eg:
          {
            mousedown : 'START_EVENT',
            mousemove : 'MOVE_EVENT',
            mouseup   : 'END_EVENT'
          }

map of event handlers. basic structure:

         type : {
          INITIAL : {
               TYPE : {
                  CAPTURING : fn(ev,_ev){}, //optional
                  BUBBLING : fn(ev,_ev){} //optional
               }
          },
          ACTIVE : {
               TYPE : {
                   CAPTURING : fn(ev,_ev){}, //optional
                   BUBBLING : fn(ev,_ev){} //optional
               }
          }
        }
